      <memberdef kind="function" id="group___overview_1ga12888981d2c1d75ffbb2a853269fc8ec" prot="public" static="yes" const="no" explicit="no" inline="no" virt="non-virtual">
        <type>void</type>
        <definition>static void ArbitrationLostHandler</definition>
        <argsstring>(XIic *InstancePtr)</argsstring>
        <name>ArbitrationLostHandler</name>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="struct_x_iic" kindref="compound">XIic</ref> *</type>
          <declname>InstancePtr</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>When multiple IIC devices attempt to use the bus simultaneously, only a single device will be able to keep control as a master. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Those devices that didn&apos;t retain control over the bus are said to have lost arbitration. When arbitration is lost, this interrupt occurs sigaling the user that the message did not get sent as expected.</para><para>This function, at arbitration lost:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Disables Tx empty, � empty and Tx error interrupts</para></listitem><listitem><para>Clears any Tx empty, � empty Rx Full or Tx error interrupts</para></listitem><listitem><para>Clears Arbitration lost interrupt,</para></listitem><listitem><para>Flush Tx FIFO</para></listitem><listitem><para>Call StatusHandler callback with the value: XII_ARB_LOST_EVENT</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_iic" kindref="compound">XIic</ref> instance to be worked on.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>None.</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
        <location file="/proj/xhdsswstaff1/bhawanas/patch_integration/auto_jobs/esw_github_doxy/git/2026.1/embeddedsw/XilinxProcessorIPLib/drivers/iic/src/xiic_multi_master.c" line="52" column="1" bodyfile="/proj/xhdsswstaff1/bhawanas/patch_integration/auto_jobs/esw_github_doxy/git/2026.1/embeddedsw/XilinxProcessorIPLib/drivers/iic/src/xiic_multi_master.c" bodystart="190" bodyend="210"/>
